overview: On January 22nd Warrior Wrestling 18 is live on FITE straight from Bendix Arena in South Bend, IN. The event features Warrior Wrestling Title Match where Will Ospreay defends his title against Brian Cage and Warrior Wrestling Lucha Title - 5 Way Scramble Match where Aramis defends his title agains 4 contenders - Sam Adonis, Gringo Loco, Drago Kid, ASF.
title: Warrior Wrestling 18
